abstract: WASHINGTON, Oct. 20--The United States Coast Guard and Cuban border authorities have worked together closely in the apprehension and prosecution of at least one American drug-smuggling suspect, the agency's logs show.

abstract: Amy Yan-lien Wang, daughter of Dr. and Mrs. Chiu-an Wang of Cambridge and Chilmark, Mass., was married in Boston yesterday to Jeremiah Evarts de Rham, son of Mr. and Mrs. Casimir de Rham of Cambridge, Mass. The Rev. Carl Scovel performed the ceremony at King's Chapel (Unitarian-Universalist.)
